Tactical Analysis: The Primal Threat

  • The Armor: 1,000+ points is staggering. Standard blades will just spark off him.

  • The Weapon: Someone with that name and armor likely carries a massive two-handed axe or hammer. One hit could "graduate" another recruit to the afterlife instantly.

  • The Strategy: You have 12 men; he has 1. You must surround and pound.
